data.description: The Iconic house with the wishing well is ready for its next owner. Located minutes from town and situated on .82  acres, this listing comes with two homes, a detached garage, pool and multiple storage options. The main home is 4  Beds/ 3 Bath, has a bonus room and is over 1,536 sq ft. The second In-law home has 2beds/1 bath, kitchen and  living area, is fully permitted and just needs finishing touches. This is the perfect place to call home, use for land, or add to your investment portfolio.
